,{"id":37568,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/19\/waswas-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":37593,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shaytan: How to repel the devil\u2019s whispering in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-\u2018Ala\u2019 reported: Uthman ibn al-\u2018As came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, Satan interferes between me, my prayer, and my recitation, confusing me.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cSuch is Satan, who is called rotten. When you sense him, then seek\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33433,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/12\/aisha-describes-prophets-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":37593,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Aisha describes the Prophet\u2019s prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would begin his prayer by exalting Allah and reciting the verses, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah, the Lord of the worlds,\u201d (1:1). When he bowed, he would not hold his head up or drop it down, but\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34843,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/27\/hadith-khtubah-al-hajah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37593,"position":4},"title":"